&lt;p&gt;All cupboards are windows.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conclusions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I. Some cupboards are racks.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;II. No cupboard is a door.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;III. No rack is a window.&lt;/p&gt;

